about.title: Hi I'm Ava! <:Ava_CatBlush:1210004576082853939>
about.description:
Ava is a versatile, open-source Discord bot designed to effortlessly meet all your entertainment needs. With Ava, entertaining your server members becomes a breeze. From music to fun utilities, Ava has everything covered. Embrace simplicity and functionality with Ava, the reliable companion for any Discord community.
### [Request Feature](https://github.com/Hamziee/Ava/issues/new) **|** [Github](https://github.com/Hamziee/Ava>) **|** [Maintainer](<https://github.com/Hamziee/>) 
[Hosted by HEO Systems](<https://heo-systems.net>)

**Developer Note:** Ava is currently a work in progress, and I am working on adding new and exciting features to Ava. Please bear in mind that this is a project of mine that I work on in my free time, so don't expect fast progress. - Hamza
